def maxProfit(prices, fee):
    n = len(prices)
    (buy, sell) = ([0] * n, [0] * n)
    buy[0] = +prices[0]
    for i in range(1, n):
        buy[i] = max(buy[i - 1], sell[i - 1] - prices[i])
        sell[i] = max(sell[i - 1], buy[i - 1] + prices[i] - fee)
    return sell[n - 1]
